Name: Last Order
About the game: Last Order is a 2D action game with pixel art style. To recover the 'Last Order' in devastated world, you'll use a variety of wire actions. Offensive wire action In Last Order, wire actions are not just about movement. Swing Wire Swing wire is an action for movement and attack with wires strung across the ceiling. Wires can cut off the enemies by passing, so it will be the primary means of attack. Dive Wire Dive Wire is an action to move at high speed to scaffolds and to enemies by elastic wire. You can break away from danger or Dive into the enemy freely. Shackle Wire Shackle Wire is an action to entangle and throw enemies or shells. It can be used not only to shoot down enemies in the distance., but also as a defense to catch shells. Growth to match your style Grow yourself according to your play style. Power if you prefer short term battles, or resilience if you are prepared for long term battles. Customize ability to fit situation Equip the order chips you obtained to gain new abilities. Use the order chip according to the situation and your style. Exploration Items are hidden in the stages where automatas are abounded. Exploration will help you find a key to your journey. Tense boss battle Bosses with a wide variety of actions are powerful, but they are not overpowered difficulty. Spot the pattern, bring down them with your skill and strategy.
